---
title: Halloumi & Pineapple Burgers with Sweet Potato Fries and Sweet Chilli Sauce
description: Chef Lizzy has really outdone herself with this harmonious blend of sweet and salty flavours. Pan-fry halloumi and pineapple until a lovely golden brown and coat in a zesty marinade made with lime, pineapple juice and salt and pepper. Frying the halloumi creates an irresistible salty snap while the pineapple rings caramelise for a wonderfully sweet taste. Top with a dollop of sweet chilli jam. Ready in 20 minutes, this dish is the solution to busy weeknights
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/halloumi-pineapple-burgers-9c9923d0-9a5a0453.jpg
